			Completes the actually running step, when the `inCondition` parameter is `TRUE`.
			Method is typically called inside a step as the transition method.
		</summary>			
	</docu>	
~]]></Comment><Parameter><Name>inCondition</Name><Comment><![CDATA[~
	<docu>
